<reference id="api_onplayerstatechanged">
    <title><ph keyref="OnPlayerStateChanged"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">Occurs when the player state changed.</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="OnPlayerStateChanged"/>
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
                <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-java" id="codeblock_oxg_z5t_3qb">void onPlayerStateChanged(AgoraRteFileInfo fileInfo, AgoraRteMediaPlayerState state, AgoraRteMediaPlayerError error);</codeblock>
                <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-objectivec" id="codeblock_pxg_z5t_3qb">- (void)AgoraRteMediaPlayer:(id&lt;AgoraRteMediaPlayerProtocol>_Nonnull)playerKit didChangedToState:(AgoraMediaPlayerState)state error:(AgoraMediaPlayerError)error rteFileInfo:(AgoraRteObjcFileInfo * _Nullable)fileInfo;</codeblock>
                <codeblock props="windows" outputclass="language-cpp" id="codeblock_qxg_z5t_3qb">virtual void OnPlayerStateChanged(const RteFileInfo&amp; current_file_info, MEDIA_PLAYER_STATE state, MEDIA_PLAYER_ERROR ec) = 0;</codeblock>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <dl outputclass="since">
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>Since</dt>
                    <dd>v</dd>
                </dlentry>
            </dl>
            <p>When the state of the player changes, the SDK triggers this callback to report the new player state and the reason or error for the change.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters"><title>Parameters</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry props="ios mac">
                    <pt>playerKit</pt>
                    <pd>The media player. See <xref keyref="IAgoraMediaPlayer"/>.</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt><ph keyref="current_file_info"/></pt>
                    <pd>The information of the played file. See <xref keyref="RteFileInfo"/>.</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>state</pt>
                    <pd>The player state after change. See <xref keyref="MEDIA_PLAYER_STATE"/>.</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt><ph keyref="ec"/></pt>
                    <pd>The player's error code. See <xref keyref="MEDIA_PLAYER_ERROR"/>.</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
